# Code Owners File

# This file defines the code ownership structure for the Malnu Backend project.
# Owners listed here will be automatically requested for review when pull requests
# modify files matching the patterns below.
#
# Format: pattern @owner1 @owner2 @owner3
# - Patterns use .gitignore syntax (see: https://git-scm.com/docs/gitignore)
# - Multiple owners can be specified
# - Use * to match any file in a directory
# - Use ** to match recursively

